@shaunviljoen @neilbosworth 

The examination form priority will be as follows:

1. Image Capture Only
2. Image Capture Only - Gauteng
3. Certificate of Fitness Examination
4. Benefit Application

Please note that it has to finish all examination forms of type Image Capture Only to reach Image Capture Only - Gauteng and all of that to move onto the next, etc.

You can go ahead and test
